sentences: Thomas Sparks (born 7 February 1986) is a Swedish-born English singer-songwriter from London.
His self-titled album was released on 11 May 2009 in the United Kingdom.
The song was included in the Ubisoft's Just Dance 3 video game and was featured in the game's trailer during the 2011 Gamescom.
He currently plays synths and guitar in Kele Okereke's solo band 'Kele'
